summary: Just watched detective pikachu!!!
body:
Just watched detective pikachu!!!

Spoilers ahead

.

.

.

Great movie!!! But since I’m too focused with cute Pokémon on screen I didn’t really notice some details that most people on tumblr have pointed out.

But I love it soo muuuch, the plot is obvious but it is very fun and I’m still surprised at the ending so gooood ❤️❤️❤️❤️

(Though what gets me is, when psyduck explode, shouldn’t it be a psychic move or something? How come the greninjas got effected? I guess the movie follows anime logic rather than the main core games logic, or maybe I’m wrong…)

Any ways 11/10 !!! I want to watch it again, but I’m not really sure if I’m allowed to

(Did anybody a cyndaquil/quilava/typhlosion in the movie?? I didn’t find it and I’m a little bummed, they’re my favorites)

summary: This is Rick Ghastly the Gengar! If memory serves correctly, my mom found him for me at a thrift store when I was in college,...
caption: This is Rick Ghastly the Gengar! If memory serves correctly, my mom found him for me at a thrift store when I was in college, and since then, he’s been a great cosplay companion. He’s a 90s Gengar plush, and I always bring him to conventions with me when I cosplay a Skull Grunt. He may have ended up in a thrift store all by himself, but now he’s a valued member of my pokefamily, and I love him a lot.

Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Bulbee Bulbasaur and Eevee fusion Normal/Grass Type Ability: Adaptibility/Chlorophyll Stats: HP - 50, Atk - 57, Def - 60, SpA -...
caption:
Bulbee

Bulbasaur and Eevee fusion

Normal/Grass Type

Ability: Adaptibility/Chlorophyll

Stats: HP - 50, Atk - 57, Def - 60, SpA - 55, SpD - 73, Spe - 57

The New Bulb Pokemon

Bulbee loves to lay in the sun and relax.  Its bud on its tail can open up if it becomes really sunny.  Although it can use sunlight to gain energy, it still needs to eat.  

I wanted to make a little bulbasaur fusion.
